title: 77 Ways to Beat Colds and Flu: A People's Medical Society Book
description:
77 Ways to Beat Colds and Flu: A People's Medical Society Book by Charles B. Inlander

Bantam | January 1, 1996 | English | ISBN: 0553574205 | 128 pages | PDF | 5 MB

Drawing on the latest scientific research, a prevention-to-treatment guide for the cold and flu season addresses such topics as vitamins and herbs, exercise, antiflu foods, and virus-proofing a home.
